<div class="bg-light p-5 rounded-3 mb-5 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Our Photography Journey</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        Combining creativity, technology, and storytelling to help new photographers find their path.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Why Photography?</h3>
        <p>
            Photography lets us freeze a moment in time. Whether it’s a landscape, a city scene,
            or a portrait, there’s always something new to learn – from exposure settings, to
            composition, to editing. It fits well with our interest in technology because modern
            cameras and editing tools are basically specialized computers with lenses.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card border-0 bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill text-primary"></i> Site Features</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Camera Database:</strong> Compare specs and prices.</li>
                    <li><strong>Location Scout:</strong> Categorized shooting spots.</li>
                    <li><strong>Resource Hub:</strong> Gear guides and expert tips.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

